<h2>What AI Marketing Agents Are (and What They Are Not)</h2>
<p>An AI marketing agent is software that plans, executes, and optimizes marketing tasks without step-by-step human instruction. You give it a goal. It figures out how to achieve that goal.</p>
<p>That last part matters. A tool needs you to press buttons. An agent needs you to set objectives.</p>
<h3>Agents vs. Tools vs. Automation</h3>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="AI marketing agents vs automation vs tools comparison" src="/images/blog/ai-marketing-agents-comparison.webp" /></p>
<p>Most marketing software falls into 3 categories. Confusing them leads to wasted budgets.</p>
