<p>The 7 highest-ROI tasks for small businesses are blog content publishing, email marketing sequences, <a href="/blog/repurpose-blog-content-social-media/">social media management</a>, ad campaign optimization, SEO monitoring, review response management, and lead scoring. Content and email are typically the best starting points.</p>
